description: NSLOCTEXT("", "D12E1D744BECDA9C9987B9AD092C4411", "The Tower Arcana has reappeared! The Academy of Arcane Scholars of Verra have discovered it and hope to claim it for research. Due to the perplexing applied magic used to craft the Intra-Sphere, the scholars find it impossible to move. But move it shall, as always. Perhaps you can find some reason for its return before it removes itself from this reality yet again.")
